basic usage using simple tone mapping:
	./tonemap imagefile outputfile -g r
tonemap with convolution
	./tonemap imagefile outputfile -g r -c
bilateral filtering
	./tonemap imagefile outputfile -b 


when the program is running press:
's' or 'S' to switch from result and original
'w' or 'W' to write to file
'q' or 'Q' or ESC to quit

